{"tid":2287404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"就係因為你開心同唔開心都一樣樣","createTime":"2020-11-15T17:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T00:27:01.000Z","uid":221696,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d55b29b12f595e03beddd6131257fc65ccd60d52","tid":2287404,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:13:12.000Z","msg":"所以先無人關心你<br />\n亦都無人可以睇穿你喺度扮堅強<br />\n<br />\n原來啲人講得好啱，識得扮弱者嘅人先有人鍚，無論佢哋點都好，都有人關心、有樹窿，有人默默喺背後支持住<br />\n<br />\n好攰呀...我都係一個有血有肉嘅人..."},{"pid":"bff8771cd1027e79238de9cdf0353484ad87541d","tid":2287404,"uid":108275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81adf8d64a997975f50e95d814e0fc529e7fb396","tid":2287404,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"},{"pid":"ca2054b700d1726f104028e5611177300e4854f7","tid":2287404,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81adf8d64a997975f50e95d814e0fc529e7fb396","tid":2287404,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:27:13.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862d53ed2b29e499ae47e71e2cb66249ce03acb1","tid":2287404,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"其實你眼中嘅弱者都好慘，人哋畀幾多佢都唔夠"},{"pid":"b84d0039c64836f008a50291f8cd0138e5770194","tid":2287404,"uid":336315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"好攰+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb27b3d86596746fd8c2e99b8e9ee992faae8c","tid":2287404,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:20:21.000Z","msg":"攬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cf21c63b60285723fd2af756cc2f92b934e08c","tid":2287404,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"難道開不開心都同樣<br />\n才稱得上是修養 <br />\n從一開始不反抗 <br />\n一生不可反抗 <br />\n怎麼可甘心這樣 <br />\n回望彼此扭曲的模樣 <br />\n遺失的拚命追上 <br />\n還想不想犧牲我 <br />\n想不想犧牲愛 <br />\n堅守這一些所謂 理想"}]}